    • Class org.rcsb.mmtf.dataholders.Group extends Object implements Serializable

      serialVersionUID:
      2880633780569899800L

      • Serialized Fields

        • groupName

          String groupName
          The group name. (e.g. HIS)

        • atomNameList

          String[] atomNameList
          The atom names. A list of strings indicating the atom names (e.g. CA for C-alpha).

        • elementList

          String[] elementList
          The element names. A list of strings indicating the element names (e.g. Ca for Calcium).

        • bondOrderList

          int[] bondOrderList
          The bond orders. A list of integers indicating the bond orders

        • bondAtomList

          int[] bondAtomList
          The bond indices (in pairs). (e.g. 0,1 means there is bond between atom 0 and 1).

        • formalChargeList

          int[] formalChargeList
          The formal charges on the atoms.

        • singleLetterCode

          char singleLetterCode
          The single letter code.

        • chemCompType

          String chemCompType
          A string (taken from the chemical component dictionary) indicating the type of the group. Corresponds to: http://mmcif.wwpdb.org/dictionaries/mmcif_pdbx.dic/Items/_chem_comp.type.html

          int[] groupsPerChain
          The internal groups per chain.

        • chainNameList

          byte[] chainNameList
          The names of the chains. Each chain is allocated four bytes. Chain names can be up to four characters long. 0 bytes indicate the end of the chain name. These are taken from the auth id.

        • chainIdList

          byte[] chainIdList
          The names of the chains. Each chain is allocated four bytes. Chain names can be up to four characters long. 0 bytes indicate the end of the chain name. These are taken from the asym id.

          String spaceGroup
          The space group.

        • unitCell

          float[] unitCell
          The unit cell.

          The bond order list.
